# Structured Spec Format — Spec-Driven Vibe Coding

> **용도**: 프로젝트 초기화 시 Claude Code가 인터뷰를 통해 빈칸을 채워나가는 스펙 템플릿.
> CLAUDE.md에 삽입하거나, `/init` 커맨드로 실행하여 프로젝트별 `PROJECT_SPEC.md`를 생성한다.

---

## 인터뷰 실행 지시문 (CLAUDE.md에 삽입)

```markdown
## Project Spec Interview Protocol

When the user runs `/spec` or asks to initialize a project spec:

1. Read the Structured Spec Template from `./templates/SPEC_TEMPLATE.md`
2. Walk through each section sequentially, asking the user to fill or confirm
3. For each section:
   - Show the section title and purpose in one sentence
   - Ask the minimum viable question set (marked 🔴 REQUIRED)
   - Offer optional deep-dive questions (marked 🟡 OPTIONAL) only if user says "more"
   - Accept "skip" to leave a section as TBD with a ⚠️ marker
   - Accept "default" to apply the recommended defaults (marked 📌 DEFAULT)
4. After all sections: generate `PROJECT_SPEC.md` in the project root
5. On subsequent code generation tasks, ALWAYS reference PROJECT_SPEC.md before writing code
6. If a code request conflicts with the spec, warn before proceeding
```

